snippet.title: My Airplane Combat Racing Game Needed an Art Update | Devlog 4
snippet.description:
Update on Snow Cannon item for my aerial combat racing game and updated a race map due to getting feedback from steam page...

Airscrew Racing is now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2336240/Airscrew_Racing/
Discord Link: https://discord.gg/b6YMEJ8tJ5

Music by: Haakon Davidson
https://www.haakondavidsen.com/

ArtForge Channel: https://www.youtube.com/@Artforge756
ArtForge Artstation: https://www.artstation.com/artforge756
